---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
import GlowLineSeparator from '@/components/ui/separator/GlowLineSeparator.astro';
const pageTitle = 'About Me';
const pageDescription = 'Learn more about Austin Crockett - a digital marketing expert specializing in SEO, content strategy, and data-driven growth.';
---

<Layout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription} pubDate={new Date()} showHeader={false}>
  <p>
    Hey! I'm Austin, a digital marketing specialist passionate about helping businesses grow through strategic, data-driven marketing.
  </p>
  <p>
    I specialize in SEO, content marketing, and analytics—combining creative strategy with measurable results. My approach focuses on understanding your audience, creating valuable content, and optimizing every touchpoint of the customer journey.
  </p>
  <p>
    With experience across B2B and B2C industries, I've helped companies increase organic traffic, improve conversion rates, and build sustainable marketing systems. Whether it's a comprehensive SEO overhaul or a targeted content campaign, I focus on strategies that deliver real business outcomes.
  </p>
  <p>
    I believe in marketing that respects the audience—no clickbait, no manipulation, just genuine value that builds trust and drives growth. When I'm not optimizing campaigns, you'll find me exploring the latest in marketing technology, writing about industry trends, or diving into analytics to uncover new opportunities.
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>Let's connect!</strong> Whether you're looking to improve your search visibility, develop a content strategy, or make sense of your marketing data, I'd love to hear about your challenges.
  </p>

  <GlowLineSeparator />

</Layout>
